Uses of Package
org.promasi.core

Packages that use org.promasi.core
org.promasi.core Implementation of the core layer 
org.promasi.core.computationalsequences Contains implementations of the IComputationalSequence. 
org.promasi.core.equations Contains implementations of the IEquation interface. 
org.promasi.core.sdobjects Contains implementations of the ISdObject class 
org.promasi.core.sdobjects.system Contains all the implementations of the ISdObject with type SdObjectType.System. 
org.promasi.shell.playmodes.singleplayerscoremode Contains implementation of the single player score mode. 
org.promasi.ui.gmtools.coredesigner Contains all the classes for the core designer ui application. 
org.promasi.ui.gmtools.coredesigner.editors Contains editors for different properties of an AbstractSdObject. 
org.promasi.ui.gmtools.coredesigner.equationbuilders Contains the editors for all IEquations. 
org.promasi.ui.gmtools.coredesigner.gef Contains implementations specific to the gef library. 
org.promasi.ui.gmtools.coredesigner.model Contains model classes for the ui.
